  "prompt": "What is the salary of vlsi fresher in India?",
  "response": "The salary of a VLSI (Very-Large-Scale Integration) fresher in India can vary depending on several factors such as the location, company, educational background, and specific skills. On average, the salary for a VLSI fresher in India typically ranges from INR 3.5 lakhs to INR 6 lakhs per annum. In some cases, salaries may be higher for those who have graduated from top engineering institutes like IITs or have specialized skills and certifications. Additionally, companies in metropolitan areas may offer higher salaries compared to those in smaller cities.",
